<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
</head>
<body class="container">

<header>
  <%- include('../partials/header'); %>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="jumbotron" style="background-image: url('images/cover.jpg');background-size: 100% 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;height: 600px;">
    <div>  
      <p class="welcome">Welcome to ADJ Hotel</p>
      <div class="availabilty" >
        <form action="/findbytype" id="roomfind" method="GET">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2  " ></div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label for="rooms" class="label">Room Types</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <!-- <div class="dropdown row dest col-md-4"> -->
              <div class="col-md-2  " ></div>
              <div class="col-md-6">

              <select name="rooms" class="type" id="room" form="roomfind">
                <option value="All">All</option>
                <option value="Standard">Standard</option>
                <option value="Luxury">Luxury</option>
                <option value="Luxury-Deluxe">Luxury Deluxe</option>
                <option value="Double">Double</option>
                <option value="Presidential Suite">Presidential Suite</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2  " >
              <input type="submit" class="find"value="Check Availability">
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="explore">
    Explore Our Rooms
  </div>
  <div class="row">
  <%
  if(roomsList.length!=0){
    var i=1;
    roomsList.forEach(function(data){
  %>
      <div class="img col-md-3" >
        <a href="/room-details?id=<%=data.type %>"id='<%data.type%>'>
        <img class="img1" src="/images/<%=data.image %>" alt="">
        <div class="desc"><%=data.type %></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    
  <% i++; })} %>
</div>


  <section class="services spad">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                  <img src="images/services/services-1.png" alt="">
                    <h4>Free Wi-Fi</h4>
                    <p>The massive investment in a hotel or resort requires constant reviews and control in order to
                        make it a successful investment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                    <img src="images/services/services-2.png" alt="">
                    <h4>Premium Pool</h4>
                    <p>Choose from 4 unique ready made concepts, let us help you create the concept perfect for you
                        or let HCA.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                    <img src="images/services/services-3.png" alt="">
                    <h4>Coffee Maker</h4>
                    <p>HCA's Owner's Representation is taking care of just these important factors, may it be
                        through regular site visits and spot checks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                    <img src="images/services/services-4.png" alt="">
                    <h4>Bar Wine</h4>
                    <p>For properties with third party management companies, HCA Consultants will as well administer
                        the terms and conditions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                    <img src="images/services/services-5.png" alt="">
                    <h4>TV HD</h4>
                    <p>We provide a critical analysis of a hotel's marketing strategy, bench-marking it against
                        industry and competitive practices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="services__item">
                    <img src="images/services/services-6.png" alt="">
                    <h4>Restaurant</h4>
                    <p>A hotel and restaurant investment deserves careful and market oriented financial planning and
                        projections.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
  <div class="client">
    <div class="client-top">
      What Our Clients Say
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      
      <div class="review col-md-4">
          <div class="text">
            "Booking the luxury Deluxe Room-City View at a really affordable price at ADJ is quite a steal."
          </div>
          <div class="cust">John Smith</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review col-md-4">
        <div class="text">
          "I will keep on recommending Agoda to my friends."
        </div>
        <div class="cust">David Miller</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review col-md-4">
        <div class="text">
          "Great customer service from the staffs."
        </div>
        <div class="cust">Jack Sparrow</div>
      </div>
    
    </div>
  </div>


  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <%- include('../partials/footer'); %>
</footer>

</body>
</html>